===Pronunciation===
אלּה / 'êlleh  / ale'-leh

===Etymology===
Prolonged from {{HH|411}}; 

===Adjective===
'''אלּה'''

# These or those: - an- (the) other; one sort, so, some, such, them, these (same), they, this, those, thus, which, who (-m).

